net.sf.mmm.util.entity.api

Interface Entity

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Serializable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    GenericEntity<ID>, MutableGenericEntity<ID>, MutableRevisionedEntity<ID>, PersistenceEntity<ID>, RevisionedEntity<ID>, SearchCriteria, TransferObject
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractGenericEntity, AbstractJpaEntity, AbstractRevisionedEntity, AbstractSearchCriteria, AbstractTransferObject, AdvancedRevisionEntity, CompositeTo, DataTo, EntityTo, JpaEntity

    public interface Entity
extends Serializable
    This is the interface for an entity or business object. It is typically a GenericEntity or a TransferObject (or both).
    Since:
    3.1.0
    Author:
    Joerg Hohwiller (hohwille at users.sourceforge.net)
